name:                loop
stack:               ( -- )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            compileonly
category:            flow control

decription:          completes a do ... loop or ?do ... loop construct, by
                     compiling a conditional branch back to do. With each
                     execution of loop will loop index be incremente by one
                     until loop limit, as passed to do or ?do, is reached.

